    <item>
      <title>特朗普给中国XI一个赢得关税打击世界的机会</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/trump-gives-china-s-xi-a-chance-to-win-over-world-hit-by-tariffs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）提高对几乎每个国家的关税的决定将对中国经济造成打击。但这也是在XI赋予罕见的开放，以加深整体关系，包括与美国在亚洲及其他地区的关键盟友。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/trump-gives-china-s-xi-a-chance-to-win-over-world-hit-by-tariffs</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Apr 2025 12:20:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普的关税将从美国股票中消除近2万亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/trump-tariffs-set-to-zap-nearly-2-trillion-from-us-stock-market</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周四交易开放时，大约将从S＆amp; P 500指数中删除约1.7万亿美元，这是因为担心唐纳德·特朗普总统的新一轮关税可能会使经济陷入衰退。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/trump-tariffs-set-to-zap-nearly-2-trillion-from-us-stock-market</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Apr 2025 12:00:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
